QuestData.Title: Wrath of the Lich King: Onwards to Northrend!
QuestData.Description: Welcome to the Wrath of the Lich King Friends and Family Alpha. Use the portals next to me to begin your journey into Northrend.$B$BYou can choose to report to the Alliance recruiter in Valiance Keep in Borean Tundra or you can go to Valgarde in Howling Fjord.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak to the Alliance Recruiter inside Valiance Keep in Borean Tundra or the one at Vengeance Landing in Howling Fjord.
